data.description: Have to see this yard in the Spring.... This completely updated home in Euclid will go quick. Priced right and all the right finishing touches are done. Just move in. Swimming pool in the deep backyard. New driveway less than 2 years old. Newer furnace, sprinkler system in the yard, & fresh paint in the two upstairs bedroom. This home is adorable. Call today to schedule your showing.....you don't want to skip this one.
